    "This survey focuses specifically on the impact and potential in the visual domain.",
    "In Fig. 3, we provide an overview of literature on supervised learning with hyperbolic geometry in computer vision.",
    "In current vision works, hyperbolic learning is mostly performed at the embedding-or classifier-level.",
    "In other words, current works rely on standard networks for feature learning and transform the output embeddings to hyperbolic space for the final learning stage.",
